com.google.api.client.googleapis.extensions.appengine.subscriptions

Class CachedAppEngineSubscriptionStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.client.googleapis.extensions.appengine.subscriptions.AppEngineSubscriptionStore
      • com.google.api.client.googleapis.extensions.appengine.subscriptions.CachedAppEngineSubscriptionStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SubscriptionStore

    public final class CachedAppEngineSubscriptionStore
extends AppEngineSubscriptionStore
    Beta
    Implementation of a persistent SubscriptionStore making use of native DataStore and the Memcache API on AppEngine.

    Implementation is thread-safe.

    On AppEngine you should prefer this SubscriptionStore over others due to performance and quota reasons.

    Example usage: 
        service.setSubscriptionStore(new CachedAppEngineSubscriptionStore());
    Since:
    1.14
    Author:
    Matthias Linder (mlinder)
